Package: intervalLevene
Type: Package
Title: Levene-Type Tests for Homogeneity of Dispersion with Interval-Valued Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    c(person("Maha", "Moussa", role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "YOUR_EMAIL"),
      person("Yan", "Sun", role = "aut"),
      person("Przemyslaw", "Grzegorzewski", role = "aut"))
Description: Implements an interval-valued extension of Levene's test for
    homogeneity of dispersion across groups using a center-radius representation,
    with a limiting reference distribution and bootstrap competitors, plus
    simulation utilities for reproducible evaluation.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
